  "description": {
    "zh": "我们正在尝试清理储备站，但这个地方极其危险，到处都是 Raider、Scav 和 PMC。此外，还有那个带着团队的前俄罗斯海军，他和他的手下装备着顶级护甲和武器，你必须小心应对。\n\n我需要一些位于基地内部的文件和科技设备。如果你能清理掉里面的威胁，我会派人进去取回这些物品。保持联系，祝你好运。",
    "en": "So, we are making an attempt to raid the military base. It's also really dangerous, full of raiders, bandits and PMC operatives. There is also this former russian marine with his guys, top tier armor and weapons so be careful when you see them.\n\nI really need some documents and technology that is located in that base, I would be very grateful if you can clean up the base a little so I can send someone else in there again to grab the stuff I need. We will stay in touch."
  },
